Class DefaultReadWorkCenterDataService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services.DefaultReadWorkCenterDataService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReadWorkCenterDataService

    @Named
public class DefaultReadWorkCenterDataService
extends Object
implements ReadWorkCenterDataService

    This service enables you to read header data, capacities, today's operations, and queueing operations for work centers.

    Business Documentation

    Reference: SAP API Business Hub

    Details:

    OData Service:API_WORK_CENTERS
    API Version:1
    Communication Scenario:Production Planning Integration (SAP_COM_0104)
    Scope Items:Material Requirements Planning (J44)
